snippet.title: Sonic 1: South Island Definitive - Teaser Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Well yes, it's been out for about a week now, but it's never too late for a trailer!

Play Sonic 1: South Island Definitive's teaser demo at this year's Chao Games Showcase!

https://www.hedgehogtechnicalinstitute.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61

Also, it seems youtube messed up the processing of this video, so for archival purposes, here's the intended 60FPS version:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OYc2MSOAQ2A
